  "intro": "<p><span><span>《从前慢》是蒋明为木心先生同名原诗谱曲的作品</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">。木心原诗语言质朴而意境深远，蒋明谱以简单绵长、悠扬动听的旋律，两相搭配，韵味全出。</span></p>\n\n<p><br></p>\n <span>《从前慢》由蒋明老搭档、知名音乐人赵照担任制作。切合蒋明舒缓而优美的旋律，赵照选用了民谣风格作品中经典的口琴与吉他搭配方式，简简单单，却抓耳又走心。</span>\n<p><br></p>\n\n<p><span>快餐年代，一切都在急速往前。木心诗中一生只爱一个人的慢时光，远去了。蒋明深情低徊、一咏三叹的歌声，让人忍不住放缓脚步，慢一点，再慢一点。</span></p>\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n<p><span>蒋明与空山乐队将于<span>7</span><span>月</span><span>16</span><span>日开启</span><span>2015</span><span>年度夏季巡演，首站柳州，而后去往南宁、贵阳、重庆、成都等</span></span><span>18<span>个</span></span><span>城市</span><span>，跨越广西、贵州、四川、河北等<span>10</span><span>个省份。</span></span><span>《从前慢》也将在巡演舞台上亮相。</span><span>2015<span>年空山巡演主题定为“如果一首歌&nbsp;不流行也不过时”，依然保有空山乐队浓郁的人文特质。这句话</span></span><span>出自</span><span>科恩兄弟的电影《醉乡民谣》，蒋明认为</span><span>它</span><span>准确表达了民谣音乐的理念，便引用来作为自己巡演的主题。</span><span>本次</span><span>巡演</span><span>，</span><span>空山乐队</span><span>还</span><span>与知名普洱茶品牌“岁月知味”联手，特别推出限量版订制茶礼“空山”，为乐迷奉上一重匠心独具的大礼。</span></p>\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n<p><span>【</span><span>岁月知味<span>.</span><span>蒋明与空山乐队</span><span>2015</span><span>夏季</span></span><span>巡演场次</span><span>安排</span><span>】&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span>7<span>月</span><span>16</span><span>日&nbsp;柳州坐夜酒馆&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>7<span>月</span><span>17</span><span>日&nbsp;南宁候朋现场</span><span>.</span><span>意酒馆&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>7<span>月</span><span>18</span><span>日&nbsp;贵阳葫芦酒吧&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>7<span>月</span><span>24</span><span>日&nbsp;重庆坚果</span><span>Livehouse&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>7<span>月</span><span>25</span><span>日&nbsp;成都小酒馆空间&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>7<span>月</span><span>30</span><span>日&nbsp;天津</span><span>13CLUB&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>7<span>月</span><span>31</span><span>日&nbsp;北京麻雀瓦舍&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>1</span><span>日&nbsp;</span></span>&nbsp;<span>宁夏沙坡头摇滚音乐节&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>5</span><span>日&nbsp;</span></span>&nbsp;<span>太原柔软时光&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>7</span><span>日&nbsp;</span></span>&nbsp;<span>石家庄地下丝绒&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>8</span><span>日</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>郑州&nbsp;<span>7&nbsp;Livehouse</span><span>（新通桥店）&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>14</span><span>日</span></span><span>烟台哈瓦那&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>15</span><span>日</span></span><span>威海梦工厂&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>21</span><span>日</span></span><span>青岛<span>Downtown&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>22</span><span>日</span></span><span>临沂老橡树<span>Livehouse&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>23</span><span>日</span></span><span>合肥<span>On&nbsp;The&nbsp;Way</span><span>（大摩店）&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>28</span><span>日</span></span><span>杭州酒球会&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span>8<span>月</span><span>29</span><span>日</span></span><span>南京斑马&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><br></p>",
